27:36.055 --> 27:37.187
(ring)

27:37.189 --> 27:39.957
¶ ain't no sunshine
when she's gone ¶

27:39.959 --> 27:42.693
No luck there,
either, ma'am.
(receiver clatters)

27:42.695 --> 27:44.895
Lauren, would you call
olivia pope for me, please?

27:44.897 --> 27:46.196
Ma'am?

27:46.198 --> 27:49.166
Olivia pope?
Would you call her, please?

27:49.168 --> 27:51.769
¶ ain't no sunshine
when she's gone ¶

